The @all_stance_mafia is always looking for members to join. lifted, lowered, trucks and suv is what we looking for. If you live in Nebraska hit my brother up @midnight5.7 he looking for members to join. If you live in another state get a hold of @all_stance_mafia to let you know your chapter president

Photo credit @midnight5.7
On Sunday got the new gear box in, just in time for more snow
Got a new gearbox for the 2000, I'm painting it so it looks nice and ready for tomorrow, thanks to @larescorp for having one ready and making sure it right
Tonight the 2000 is having the gearbox removed because the output shaft seal is leaking really bad due to the seal is crooked
Happy new years to everybody, I appreciate all of the followers, all the likes for this year hopefully next year is better than ever
I usually don't post much with the four wheeler because i don't change much maybe something once a year, but this year i got hand guards
Come spring the 95 is getting a new black grill and a roll pan
Happy holidays to everybody from me, come spring the 95 will keep getting better
Got the truck cleaned yesterday, it so pretty when it's nice and clean
If your not following @carsinbarns you should, plus the 95 is on his page thanks to him
Just another round of snow and another truck pic
I can't believe it's been over a year and the 95 has came a long way since then
The day after I have the truck looking good, mother nature decides it's time to snow
Who doesn't like looking at a clean truck

I was going through the pictures here I got on the phone, this is more than likely one of many reasons why I have my 95, this was my father's 2000 Chevrolet C/K 3500 single axle with the 454 big block from the factory, I grew up around this truck for 16 years of my life and it was a very emotional day when it got traded in, this is the truck that started my love and passion for any 88 - 98 GM truck
Been collecting parts and pieces for the 95 can't wait till spring
Happy Turkey day, just another truck pic
Another snowfall before I punch the clock to leave work
Had the 2000 washed the other day after working  on the front suspension for the last month
The pictures on top are from 1999 and just recently with the previous owner put the truck back in the same spot 20 years later
Go over to @all_stance_mafia story and please go vote for me so I can keep going rounds
#allstancesaturdays
Today the 95 is being put away for  winter, I have pictures that were recently done but have not looked  at them yet
Try to get one last show in for the season before the 95 here gets park for the winter
